WEBVTT

00:00:00.667 --> 00:00:02.536
Narrator: PREVIOUSLY
ON <i>YU-GI-OH...</i>

00:00:02.536 --> 00:00:04.838
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,
AND FELLOW DUELISTS,

00:00:04.838 --> 00:00:11.178
THE CREATOR OF DUEL MONSTERS,
MR. MAXIMILLION PEGASUS!

00:00:11.178 --> 00:00:12.346
Yugi:
WHO ARE YOU?

00:00:12.346 --> 00:00:13.614
MY NAME IS SHADI.

00:00:13.614 --> 00:00:14.948
BE ON YOUR GUARD.

00:00:14.948 --> 00:00:16.216
FOR WHOEVER THE THIEF IS

00:00:16.216 --> 00:00:18.352
WHO STOLE PEGASUS'
MILLENNIUM ITEM,

00:00:18.352 --> 00:00:20.621
HE WILL ALSO COME
SEEKING YOURS.

00:00:20.621 --> 00:00:22.589
Yugi:
IT'S TIME! GO!

00:00:22.589 --> 00:00:24.958
SLIFER,
THE SKY DRAGON,

00:00:24.958 --> 00:00:25.959
ATTACK!

00:00:35.035 --> 00:00:37.170
♪ YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE,
YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:37.170 --> 00:00:39.106
♪ YOUR MOVE, YOUR MOVE ♪

00:00:45.178 --> 00:00:47.014
♪ YU-GI-OH, YU-GI ♪

00:01:08.101 --> 00:01:11.338
IT'S TIME
TO DUEL!

00:01:25.419 --> 00:01:28.755
♪ YU-GI-OH! ♪

00:01:32.459 --> 00:01:34.595
Man on P.A.: ATTENTION
BATTLE CITY FINALISTS...

00:01:34.595 --> 00:01:36.630
WITH THE COMPLETION
OF THE OPENING DUEL,

00:01:36.630 --> 00:01:38.765
THERE WILL BE A HALF
HOUR INTERMISSION.

00:01:38.765 --> 00:01:40.434
AT THE END OF THIS INTERMISSION,

00:01:40.434 --> 00:01:42.703
ALL REMAINING FINALISTS
ARE INSTRUCTED

00:01:42.703 --> 00:01:44.972
TO REPORT TO
THE MAIN CONCOURSE

00:01:44.972 --> 00:01:48.575
FOR THE SELECTION OF THE NEXT
BATTLE CITY FINALS MATCH-UP.

00:01:48.575 --> 00:01:49.576
WE HAVE TO HELP
BAKURA!

00:01:49.576 --> 00:01:51.612
AND...LAND THIS THING!

00:01:51.612 --> 00:01:52.913
SO, LET'S FIND KAIBA.

00:01:52.913 --> 00:01:54.748
HE MUST BE IN ONE
OF THESE ROOMS!

00:01:54.748 --> 00:01:57.217
YOU GUYS, THIS IS
A RESTRICTED AREA!

00:01:57.217 --> 00:01:58.318
Joey:
HEY, MOKUBA!

00:01:58.318 --> 00:01:59.920
WHERE IS
YOUR BROTHER?

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.622
THAT'S HIS ROOM.

00:02:01.622 --> 00:02:03.457
BUT YOU DON'T WANT
TO DISTURB HIM.

00:02:03.457 --> 00:02:05.626
HEY! OPEN THE DOOR!

00:02:05.626 --> 00:02:06.627
LET'S GO, KAIBA!

00:02:06.627 --> 00:02:07.694
ARE YOU NUTS!?

00:02:07.694 --> 00:02:08.929
HE'S PREPARING
FOR A DUEL!

00:02:08.929 --> 00:02:10.097
STOP IT!

00:02:10.097 --> 00:02:11.565
I'M TALKING
TO YOU, KAIBA!

00:02:11.565 --> 00:02:14.434
GET OUT HERE NOW...

00:02:14.434 --> 00:02:16.536
IF IT ISN'T WHEELER.

00:02:16.536 --> 00:02:18.639
YOU'RE LUCKY TO EVEN
BE IN MY TOURNAMENT,

00:02:18.639 --> 00:02:21.274
AND YET YOU INSIST ON MAKING
A NUISANCE OF YOURSELF

00:02:21.274 --> 00:02:23.443
OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

00:02:23.443 --> 00:02:25.512
THAT DID IT!

00:02:25.512 --> 00:02:27.147
HEY, THIS IS NO TIME
TO PICK A FIGHT,

00:02:27.147 --> 00:02:29.516
SO JUST
CALM DOWN, MAN!

00:02:29.516 --> 00:02:31.451
Yugi: KAIBA, YOU'VE
GOT TO HELP US!

00:02:31.451 --> 00:02:33.220
NOW WHAT?
BAKURA'S HURT.

00:02:33.220 --> 00:02:34.788
WE HAVE TO LAND NOW!

00:02:34.788 --> 00:02:37.024
HE NEEDS TO SEE A DOCTOR
RIGHT AWAY, KAIBA!

00:02:37.024 --> 00:02:40.794
YOU'RE ASKING ME TO
DO THE IMPOSSIBLE.

00:02:40.794 --> 00:02:43.230
WE CAN'T MAKE
AN UNSCHEDULED STOP.

00:02:43.230 --> 00:02:45.766
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND,
BAKURA NEEDS HELP!

00:02:45.766 --> 00:02:46.833
Tristan: HE'S BEEN
UNCONSCIOUS

00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:48.135
SINCE LOSING
HIS DUEL!

00:02:48.135 --> 00:02:50.170
AND IF HE GETS ANY WORSE
THAN HE IS RIGHT NOW,

00:02:50.170 --> 00:02:51.705
YOU'LL BE RESPONSIBLE!

00:02:51.705 --> 00:02:54.041
THAT'S A RISK
I'M WILLING TO TAKE.

00:02:54.041 --> 00:02:55.108
PLEASE, KAIBA.

00:02:55.108 --> 00:02:56.376
THIS IS REALLY
IMPORTANT!

00:02:56.376 --> 00:02:58.145
SHOW SOME COMPASSION.

00:02:58.145 --> 00:02:59.212
PRETTY PLEASE.

00:02:59.212 --> 00:03:02.215
Duke: HOW CAN YOU SAY
NO TO THAT FACE!?

00:03:02.215 --> 00:03:03.784
SEREN--
SERENITY'S
RIGHT!

00:03:03.784 --> 00:03:05.118
HE SHOULDN'T HAVE
LEFT THE HOSPITAL

00:03:05.118 --> 00:03:06.319
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

00:03:06.319 --> 00:03:09.022
THIS IS BAKURA'S
OWN FAULT.

00:03:09.022 --> 00:03:10.190
KAIBA, PLEASE!

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:11.391
ISN'T SOMEONE'S HEALTH

00:03:11.391 --> 00:03:13.560
MORE IMPORTANT THAN
YOUR SILLY GAME?

00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:14.995
Tristan: LISTEN
TO HER, WILL YOU!

00:03:14.995 --> 00:03:16.096
SHE'S GOT
A GOOD POINT!

00:03:16.096 --> 00:03:18.965
WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU?

00:03:18.965 --> 00:03:20.934
Joey: I'VE HAD ENOUGH
OF THIS ATTITUDE, KAIBA!

00:03:20.934 --> 00:03:22.836
FIND A WAY TO LAND
THIS BLIMP PRONTO,

00:03:22.836 --> 00:03:24.071
OR GET READY TO SAY "HI"

00:03:24.071 --> 00:03:25.839
TO THE BUSINESS END
OF MY FIST!

00:03:25.839 --> 00:03:29.376
I TOLD YOU WE'RE NOT
LANDING, WHEELER.

00:03:29.376 --> 00:03:30.911
THEN LET'S DANCE!

00:03:30.911 --> 00:03:33.046
HEY, COME BACK!

00:03:33.046 --> 00:03:34.314
RELAX,
JOEY!

00:03:34.314 --> 00:03:36.016
WHAT GIVES?

00:03:36.016 --> 00:03:38.719
SEND A MEDICAL TEAM
TO BAKURA'S ROOM.

00:03:38.719 --> 00:03:40.353
GOOD CALL, SETO.

00:03:40.353 --> 00:03:42.055
KAIBA CORP'S ON-BOARD
MEDICAL STAFF

00:03:42.055 --> 00:03:43.690
HAS BETTER TRAINING
THAN THE DOCTORS

00:03:43.690 --> 00:03:45.592
AT MOST
HOSPITALS DO.

00:03:45.592 --> 00:03:47.594
BAKURA'S IN
GOOD HANDS HERE.

00:03:47.594 --> 00:03:50.630
Serenity: I HOPE MOKUBA'S RIGHT
ABOUT THE DOCTORS ONBOARD.

00:03:50.630 --> 00:03:51.865
Tristan: HEY, IT
WAS GREAT HOW YOU

00:03:51.865 --> 00:03:53.266
STOOD UP TO
KAIBA, SERENITY!

00:03:53.266 --> 00:03:56.470
I FELT THE EXACT SAME
WAY YOU DID BACK THERE!

00:03:56.470 --> 00:03:58.739
AND I HAVE NEVER BEEN
SO MOVED BY A SPEECH

00:03:58.739 --> 00:04:00.307
IN MY LIFE, SERENITY,

00:04:00.307 --> 00:04:03.310
IT'S LIKE YOUR WORDS
CAME RIGHT OUT OF
THE MOUTH OF AN ANGEL!

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:05.245
SO, DO YOU THINK THAT
BAKURA'S GONNA BE OK

00:04:05.245 --> 00:04:07.781
IN THE HANDS OF KAIBA'S
QUACKS OR WHAT, YUG?

00:04:07.781 --> 00:04:09.082
I HOPE SO.

00:04:09.082 --> 00:04:10.817
HEY, WE STILL
HAVE TO FIND

00:04:10.817 --> 00:04:12.619
BAKURA'S MISSING
MILLENNIUM RING.

00:04:12.619 --> 00:04:13.887
IT SHOULDN'T BE
THAT DIFFICULT

00:04:13.887 --> 00:04:14.921
IF WE SPLIT UP,
RIGHT?

00:04:14.921 --> 00:04:16.490
DON'T YOU GUYS
WORRY ABOUT IT.

00:04:16.490 --> 00:04:17.891
JUST LEAVE
THE MILLENNIUM RING

00:04:17.891 --> 00:04:20.360
TO ME AND DEVLIN.

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:21.795
YOU TWO SHOULD
STAY FOCUSED

00:04:21.795 --> 00:04:23.830
ON THE NEXT ROUND
OF THE FINALS.

00:04:23.830 --> 00:04:25.832
IT'S OK,
TRISTAN, REALLY.

00:04:25.832 --> 00:04:28.135
NO, I'M NOT GONNA LET MY
FRIENDS GET DISTRACTED

00:04:28.135 --> 00:04:30.504
BEFORE THE BIGGEST DUEL
OF THEIR LIVES.

00:04:30.504 --> 00:04:32.806
PLUS, IT'LL GIVE ME
AND DUKE SOMETHING TO DO!

00:04:32.806 --> 00:04:35.408
PERFECT, SERENITY AND I
WILL SEARCH UPSTAIRS!

00:04:35.408 --> 00:04:36.443
Tristan:
FORGET IT!

00:04:36.443 --> 00:04:38.478
YOU'RE COMING
WITH ME, DEVLIN.

00:04:38.478 --> 00:04:40.313
BUT I WAS A--
ZIP IT!

00:04:40.313 --> 00:04:42.549
THAT MILLENNIUM RING'S
NOT GONNA FIND ITSELF,

00:04:42.549 --> 00:04:44.851
SO YOU AND I HAVE TO
WORK TOGETHER, DUDE!

00:04:44.851 --> 00:04:46.386
COME ON, WE GOT
WORK TO DO!

00:04:46.386 --> 00:04:48.088
[MUFFLED]
SERENITY! SERENITY!

00:04:49.923 --> 00:04:51.525
IT'S NICE
TO SEE THEM
GETTING ALONG,

00:04:51.525 --> 00:04:53.260
YOU KNOW?
YEAH, SURE.

00:04:53.260 --> 00:04:54.327
I JUST HOPE
THEY HAVE LUCK

00:04:54.327 --> 00:04:55.896
FINDING BAKURA'S
MILLENNIUM RING.

00:05:01.067 --> 00:05:04.137
Duke: I DON'T SEE A THING
UP HERE, LET'S MOVE ON.

00:05:04.137 --> 00:05:05.272
Tristan: WHY DON'T YOU
STOP COMPLAINING

00:05:05.272 --> 00:05:06.773
AND CHECK IN
THAT CORNER?

00:05:06.773 --> 00:05:09.609
THERE'S NOTHING UP HERE
BUT HOT AIR.

00:05:09.609 --> 00:05:11.545
AND ALL OF IT'S COMING
FROM YOU, TRISTAN!

00:05:11.545 --> 00:05:12.712
SO, LAY OFF!

00:05:12.712 --> 00:05:14.247
LISTEN, LOVER-BOY,

00:05:14.247 --> 00:05:15.348
YOU'VE BEEN A PAIN
IN MY NECK

00:05:15.348 --> 00:05:17.651
SINCE THE DAY
WE RAN INTO YOU!

00:05:17.651 --> 00:05:19.152
IT'S TIME FOR YOU
TO CHILL OUT

00:05:19.152 --> 00:05:21.521
AND REMEMBER WHY
WE'RE HERE, OK?

00:05:21.521 --> 00:05:23.623
WHAT'S THAT SUPPOSED
TO MEAN, TOUGH GUY?

00:05:23.623 --> 00:05:25.892
I'M TELLING YOU TO LAY
OFF SERENITY, DEVLIN.

00:05:25.892 --> 00:05:27.093
GIVE THE GIRL
SOME SPACE!

00:05:27.093 --> 00:05:28.528
WHA...?

00:05:28.528 --> 00:05:30.730
DO YOU KNOW WHAT
YOUR PROBLEM IS, TRISTAN?

00:05:30.730 --> 00:05:32.199
YOU'RE AFRAID.

00:05:32.199 --> 00:05:34.234
AFRAID THAT SERENITY
MIGHT LIKE ME

00:05:34.234 --> 00:05:36.069
INSTEAD OF LIKING YOU.

00:05:36.069 --> 00:05:38.939
HUH? NO, I'M NOT.

00:05:38.939 --> 00:05:42.008
IT'S NOT MY FAULT
IF THE LADIES CAN'T
RESIST DUKE DEVLIN...

00:05:42.008 --> 00:05:44.811
I GUESS I COULD TURN
THE CHARM DOWN...

00:05:44.811 --> 00:05:46.546
DON'T PUSH ME!

00:05:46.546 --> 00:05:48.181
BUT WHAT DO YOU EXPECT?

00:05:48.181 --> 00:05:50.116
YOU'RE NOT EVEN A DUELIST,

00:05:50.116 --> 00:05:51.751
JUST SOME WANNABE
CHEERLEADER

00:05:51.751 --> 00:05:53.620
WHO'S ALWAYS YELLING
FROM THE SIDELINES.

00:05:53.620 --> 00:05:56.189
"GO, YUGI!
GO, JOEY!"

00:05:56.189 --> 00:05:58.058
IT'S REALLY
KIND OF PATHETIC!

00:05:58.058 --> 00:05:59.759
GIRLS DIG MEN OF ACTION.

00:05:59.759 --> 00:06:00.827
AND YOU, WELL...

00:06:00.827 --> 00:06:02.696
YOU'RE NO MAN OF ACTION.

00:06:02.696 --> 00:06:03.797
WHAT?!

00:06:03.797 --> 00:06:05.232
I'LL SHOW YOU ACTION!

00:06:05.232 --> 00:06:08.068
SO, LET'S GO!

00:06:08.068 --> 00:06:09.936
[BOTH SCREAMING]

00:06:11.071 --> 00:06:12.505
OH, NO!

00:06:12.505 --> 00:06:16.176
[SCREAMING]

00:06:16.176 --> 00:06:17.377
Tristan: GOTCHA!

00:06:17.377 --> 00:06:21.014
WHATEVER YOU DO, DUKE,
DON'T LOOK DOWN!

00:06:25.919 --> 00:06:29.589
HOLD ON, DUKE!
I GOT YA!

00:06:29.589 --> 00:06:30.657
YEAH?!

00:06:30.657 --> 00:06:32.192
YOU GOT ME HERE
IN THE FIRST PLACE!

00:06:32.192 --> 00:06:34.427
RELAX, I HAVE
A PLAN, NO JOKE!

00:06:34.427 --> 00:06:36.029
I CAN'T WAIT
FOR THIS ONE!

00:06:36.029 --> 00:06:37.597
SOMEONE! ANYONE!

00:06:37.597 --> 00:06:38.598
HELP US!

00:06:38.598 --> 00:06:40.200
THAT'S YOUR PLAN?!

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:42.068
PLEASE!
WE NEED HELP!

00:06:42.068 --> 00:06:43.403
ANYONE OUT THERE?

00:06:43.403 --> 00:06:45.071
HELP! PLEASE!

00:06:45.071 --> 00:06:46.439
MAN!

00:06:46.439 --> 00:06:47.874
WE BETTER HOPE
SOMEONE HEARS US

00:06:47.874 --> 00:06:49.943
'CAUSE IT'S
A LONG WAY DOWN!

00:06:49.943 --> 00:06:51.511
[STRAINING]

00:06:51.511 --> 00:06:53.246
HOW'S YOUR GRIP?

00:06:53.246 --> 00:06:55.081
WELL, NOW THAT YOU
BRING IT UP...

00:06:55.081 --> 00:06:56.082
...NOT GOOD!

00:06:56.082 --> 00:06:57.884
MY HAND'S GONE NUMB!

00:06:57.884 --> 00:06:59.052
DON'T GIVE IN!

00:06:59.052 --> 00:07:00.120
FIGHT IT!

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:01.388
I'M TRYING!

00:07:01.388 --> 00:07:02.622
[GROANING]

00:07:02.622 --> 00:07:04.057
I'M SORRY, DUKE!

00:07:04.057 --> 00:07:05.625
DON'T LET GO!

00:07:05.625 --> 00:07:06.693
TOO LATE...

00:07:06.693 --> 00:07:08.528
MY HAND
IS SLIPPING!

00:07:09.729 --> 00:07:12.399
[GRUNTS]

00:07:12.399 --> 00:07:14.601
WHAT'S GOING ON UP THERE?

00:07:14.601 --> 00:07:16.336
SOMEONE'S GOT ME!

00:07:16.336 --> 00:07:18.104
HEY!

00:07:18.104 --> 00:07:20.106
CAN YOU PULL US UP?

00:07:20.106 --> 00:07:23.176
THANKS! I OWE YOU ONE.

00:07:23.176 --> 00:07:25.245
WE'RE GONNA
BE OK, DUKE!

00:07:25.245 --> 00:07:28.548
[BOTH GROANING]

00:07:28.548 --> 00:07:30.116
Duke: THAT
WAS NOT FUN!

00:07:30.116 --> 00:07:31.651
WHO ARE YOU?

00:07:31.651 --> 00:07:33.053
YOU SAVED OUR LIVES!

00:07:33.053 --> 00:07:34.654
HOW CAN WE REPAY YOU?

00:07:34.654 --> 00:07:35.789
HUH?

00:07:35.789 --> 00:07:37.190
WHERE DID HE GO?

00:07:37.190 --> 00:07:39.092
SOMETHING WRONG,
TRISTAN?

00:07:39.092 --> 00:07:40.193
HE'S...GONE.

00:07:40.193 --> 00:07:41.428
THE GUY IN
THE WHITE BATHROBE

00:07:41.428 --> 00:07:43.496
WHO JUST SAVED
BOTH OUR HIDES!

00:07:43.496 --> 00:07:45.699
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

00:07:45.699 --> 00:07:48.768
THE GUY WHO--
OH, NEVER MIND.

00:07:48.768 --> 00:07:50.503
LET'S GO FIND THE REST
OF THE GANG.

00:07:53.239 --> 00:07:54.441
Yugi, thinking: WELL,
I WON THE FIRST DUEL

00:07:54.441 --> 00:07:55.875
OF THE BATTLE
CITY FINALS...

00:07:55.875 --> 00:07:57.310
THANKS TO MY
EGYPTIAN GOD CARD,

00:07:57.310 --> 00:07:58.878
SLIFER, THE SKY DRAGON.

00:07:58.878 --> 00:08:00.714
BUT I STILL NEED TO
BE CAREFUL WITH IT.

00:08:00.714 --> 00:08:02.816
IT SEEMS LIKE IT
HAS REAL POWERS--

00:08:02.816 --> 00:08:04.417
BEYOND THIS GAME.

00:08:04.417 --> 00:08:06.186
[GASPS]

00:08:08.154 --> 00:08:09.856
I REMEMBER YOU,
YOU'RE SHADI!

00:08:09.856 --> 00:08:11.024
YES.

00:08:11.024 --> 00:08:12.158
AND YOU'VE LEARNED MUCH

00:08:12.158 --> 00:08:14.260
SINCE WE FIRST MET
IN DUELIST KINGDOM, YUGI.

00:08:14.260 --> 00:08:15.829
YOU'RE BEGINNING
TO UNDERSTAND YOUR FATE,

00:08:15.829 --> 00:08:17.530
AND ITS RELATION
TO THE PAST.

00:08:17.530 --> 00:08:18.999
A FATE THAT INTERTWINES WITH

00:08:18.999 --> 00:08:21.835
THAT OF THE SPIRIT WHO DWELLS
WITHIN YOUR MILLENNIUM PUZZLE.

00:08:21.835 --> 00:08:23.169
WELL...

00:08:23.169 --> 00:08:24.304
I KNOW
A LITTLE BIT...

00:08:24.304 --> 00:08:26.806
LIKE YAMI WAS
AN ANCIENT PHARAOH.

00:08:26.806 --> 00:08:28.375
THAT IS CORRECT.

00:08:28.375 --> 00:08:30.877
AND TOGETHER YOU MUST
SAVE THE EARTH.

00:08:30.877 --> 00:08:33.246
FROM AN ANCIENT
EVIL, I KNOW.

00:08:33.246 --> 00:08:35.048
BUT ARE YOU HERE
TO EXPLAIN HOW?

00:08:35.048 --> 00:08:36.916
'CAUSE I'M
STILL CONFUSED.

00:08:36.916 --> 00:08:40.987
I AM BUT THE GUARDIAN OF
THE 7 MILLENNIUM ITEMS.

00:08:40.987 --> 00:08:42.522
I AM HERE BECAUSE I SENSED

00:08:42.522 --> 00:08:45.358
A DISTURBANCE IN THE MYSTIC
ALIGNMENT ONCE AGAIN.

00:08:45.358 --> 00:08:46.693
[GASPS]

00:08:46.693 --> 00:08:50.096
ALL 7 ITEMS ARE
ON BOARD THIS VESSEL,

00:08:50.096 --> 00:08:52.365
AS WELL AS THE 3
EGYPTIAN GOD CARDS--

00:08:52.365 --> 00:08:53.833
WHICH MEANS
ALL OF THE OBJECTS

00:08:53.833 --> 00:08:56.169
CAPABLE OF SAVING
AND DESTROYING THE WORLD

00:08:56.169 --> 00:08:57.237
ARE RIGHT HERE.

00:08:57.237 --> 00:08:58.872
REALLY!?

00:08:58.872 --> 00:09:00.240
MMM...

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:02.609
AND THE EARTH'S SAFETY
RESTS WITH YOU, YUGI.

00:09:02.609 --> 00:09:04.044
HEED MY WORDS:

00:09:04.044 --> 00:09:05.945
IF THE WRONG
INDIVIDUALS WERE TO

00:09:05.945 --> 00:09:08.314
GAIN CONTROL OF ANY OF
THE MILLENNIUM ITEMS

00:09:08.314 --> 00:09:10.350
OR ONE OF
THE EGYPTIAN GOD CARDS...

00:09:10.350 --> 00:09:12.886
THE RESULTS COULD
BE CATASTROPHIC.

00:09:12.886 --> 00:09:14.521
IT NEARLY HAPPENED
ONCE BEFORE

00:09:14.521 --> 00:09:16.689
WHEN PEGASUS CREATED
DUEL MONSTERS.

00:09:16.689 --> 00:09:18.358
IT DID!?
BUT HOW?

00:09:18.358 --> 00:09:21.294
WELL, IT ALL BEGAN WHEN
MAXIMILLION PEGASUS

00:09:21.294 --> 00:09:23.063
FIRST ARRIVED IN EGYPT.

00:09:23.063 --> 00:09:26.900
HE WAS SEARCHING FOR A METHOD OF
REUNITING WITH HIS LOST LOVE.

00:09:26.900 --> 00:09:28.968
HIS QUEST BROUGHT HIM TO ME,

00:09:28.968 --> 00:09:31.037
AND I PRESENTED HIM
WITH THE MILLENNIUM EYE,

