00:20:11.143 --> 00:20:13.813
I KNOW THERE'S STILL
GOOD WITHIN YOU.

00:20:13.813 --> 00:20:16.649
SISTER,
FOR YOU!

00:20:17.817 --> 00:20:18.818
Shadi: ISHIZU,

00:20:18.818 --> 00:20:20.686
IT'S HAPPENING.

00:20:20.686 --> 00:20:21.687
SHADI.

00:20:21.687 --> 00:20:22.822
WITH SO MUCH AT STAKE,

00:20:22.822 --> 00:20:24.957
I SHOULD HAVE KNOWN
YOU'D BE HERE.

00:20:24.957 --> 00:20:26.025
YES.

00:20:26.025 --> 00:20:27.460
EVIL ONCE AGAIN
WALKS THE EARTH,

00:20:27.460 --> 00:20:29.462
BRINGING MADNESS
IN ITS WAKE.

00:20:29.462 --> 00:20:31.230
I JUST NEVER
THOUGHT MY OWN BROTHER

00:20:31.230 --> 00:20:33.466
WOULD BE THE MEDIUM
FOR THIS EVIL.

00:20:33.466 --> 00:20:34.967
OH, MARIK.

00:20:34.967 --> 00:20:38.003
THE WORLD MUST BE SAVED,
BUT AT WHAT COST?

00:20:38.003 --> 00:20:41.006
I DON'T WANT TO
LOSE MY BROTHER!

00:20:41.006 --> 00:20:43.242
[GASPS]

00:20:46.979 --> 00:20:50.049
Marik: I'LL KEEP BAKURA'S
MILLENNIUM RING FOR NOW.

00:20:50.049 --> 00:20:54.186
AND I'LL ALSO
MAINTAIN OCCASIONAL
CONTROL OVER TEA'S MIND.

00:20:55.755 --> 00:20:57.790
MY KEY SHIELDS ME
FROM HER SIGHT.

00:20:57.790 --> 00:20:58.891
WAIT...

00:20:58.891 --> 00:21:01.293
THE MYSTIC DISTURBANCE
THAT BROUGHT ME HERE

00:21:01.293 --> 00:21:03.095
IS STRONGEST
IN THIS ROOM.

00:21:03.095 --> 00:21:05.898
I FEEL THAT THE DESTINIES
OF CERTAIN MILLENNIUM ITEMS

00:21:05.898 --> 00:21:07.366
ARE BEING MANIPULATED.

00:21:07.366 --> 00:21:09.735
AND UNTIL HARMONY
IS RESTORED,

00:21:09.735 --> 00:21:11.771
THE WORLD WILL BE
IN GRAVE PERIL.

